title: Detwinner 2.03.003 (Install + Portable)
description:
Detwinner 2.03.003 (Install + Portable)

About this release

Release date: 30 May 2016
OS: Windows XP SP2/Vista/7/8/10 (32-bit/64-bit)
Install: run installer, do not launch the app, copy cracked file to installation directory and overwrite, launch application, go to About and disable update check
Portable: cracked, update check disabled, simply unpack and run executable

About Detwinner

Detwinner is the simplest and fastest tool for removing duplicate files from your Windows PC.

- search for identical documents, video, music, pictures;
- locate similar images;
- increase free space on your hard disk or pen drive.

Benefits of the registered version: unlimited number of files to search among;

Remove duplicate files and similar images in three easy steps:

1. Choose search options and press Search button.
You can search for either exact duplicates (100% byte-to-byte match is ensured by the special hash function) or similar images (Detwinner generates groups of images that look alike using similarity level specified by you). You can also narrow your search by specifying file dates, attributes and masks.

2. Review found duplicates and select files to be removed.
Smart and regexp-based selection tools provide numerous options for batch selection of files that should be deleted. Instant preview allows you to be confident in your choice.

3. Press Delete button.
Files can be deleted permanently, to Recycle Bin or moved to the backup folder.

Homepage http://neatdecisions.com/products/detwinner/
